		height: 20px;
		background: #d1fae5;
		color: #065f46;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	/* Resources Section */
	.cms-resources {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
		color: white;
	}

	.resources-content {
		max-width: 1200px;
